\title{Vector Processing Unit}
\p{A core component of the [TPU architecture](NZZ7) responsible for elementwise operations.}
\ul{
  \li{2D [SIMD](Q7ZD) execution, where each of 1024 \em{sites} execute same program in lockstep.}
  \li{Each site contains 4 ALUs, enabling 4096 FLOPs.}
  \li{Fed a 8x128 [Vector Register](OGCRO) in one cycle.}
}
